{"id":9275,"content":"<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><?xml:namespace prefix = \"o\" ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\"></FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">近来，本刊读者和微博网友来电来函或在微博上私信留言，咨询明年《炎黄春秋》杂志订阅、合订本邮购、《炎黄春秋》官方微博上文章的发布等问题。现统一回复如下：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">、明年（</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2014</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年）《炎黄春秋》杂志从</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">11</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">月初即可在当地邮局订阅。明年杂志的定价有所调整，每期定价</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">10</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">元，全年</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">12</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">期</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">120</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">元。如从本刊发行部邮购，</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">10</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">月份就可办理。建议最好在当地邮局订阅，收刊方便快捷。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">２、《炎黄春秋》杂志</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2013</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年合订本仍分上下两卷。按往年惯例，</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2013</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年合订本在明年</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">3</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">月份才能印制完成。今年</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">12</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">月初将在《炎黄春秋》杂志和炎黄春秋网上发布预定通告，届时请有邮购《炎黄春秋》杂志合订本意向的读者留意。炎黄春秋杂志社发行部是邮购《炎黄春秋》杂志合订本的惟一渠道。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">3</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">、《炎黄春秋》杂志及其合订本的订阅、邮购办法，在炎黄春秋网（</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">www.yhcqw.com</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">）首页“订阅邮购”一栏中有详细介绍：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><A href=\"http://www.yhcqw.com/mall/zybdy/index.html\"><FONT color=#800080 face=\"Times New Roman\">http://www.yhcqw.com/mall/zybdy/index.html</FONT></A><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\"> </FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">；《炎黄春秋》官方微博中也有此内容的相关链接。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">4</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">、《炎黄春秋》在几大门户网站均开设有官方微博。当期杂志的全部文章先后都会在官方微博上全文或摘要（长微博）发布，往期杂志的精华文章也会通过微博链接供关注《炎黄春秋》的广大读者阅读。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt\"></FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">5</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">、为保持《炎黄春秋》杂志纸样版原貌，《炎黄春秋》官方微博的发布范围将限定在仅发布本刊原创文章，不作其他转发。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN>2013</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">9</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">15</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">日</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">.<o:p></o:p></FONT></SPAN></P>","title":"答读者问（2013.9.15.）","time":1379251982000}